          "settings": {
            "description_heading": "Introduction"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_PAyNwP": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Miniature Planar Magnetic Tweeter",
            "content": "<p>The Z02's hybrid design features a specially designed miniature planar magnetic tweeter embedded in a 3D-printed shell, eliminating sound pressure decay and resonance typical of traditional tubed balanced armature designs. This tweeter enhances high-frequency performance with precision, extended range, and low distortion, while its compact size, fast transient response, and wide dispersion ensure realistic sound reproduction and a consistent soundstage. Its durable, robust design resists environmental changes, and it synergizes effectively with the dynamic armature drivers in multi-driver systems, delivering a well-balanced and high-fidelity audio profile.</p>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_n38dzJ": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "10mmGraphene Dynamic Driver",
            "content": "<p>The newly designed dynamic driver features an ultra-thin,<br/>rigid film diaphragm crafted from graphene material. Paired with a<br/>physical low-pass filter, it operates within a minimal overlapping frequency<br/>range, complementing the planar tweeter. With a meticulously arranged driver<br/>positioning and an advanced 3D-printed acoustic chamber design, AAW achieves<br/>enhanced coherence, reduces phase shift, and optimizes the timing of audio<br/>signal delivery for a more precise and immersive listening experience.</p>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_HffCBq": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "3D Printed Enclosure and Precision Engineering",
            "content": "<p>With a wholly digitized design process, Z02 employs AAW 3rd<br/>generation digital enclosure and acoustic chamber design. Driver and nozzle<br/>placements are simulated hundreds of iterations to determine the ideal phasing<br/>and response. It is then 3D printed to precision to maintain consistency in<br/>mass production.</p>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_XefaKL": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Accessories and Warranty",
            "content": "<p>48\" Null Audio Brevity Pro Plus OCC Detachable Cable<br/>AAW Carrying Case<br/>3 Pairs AAW Short Stem Foam Tips(S/M/L)<br/>6 Pairs AAW Assorted Silicone Tips (S/M/LX2)<br/>1 Year Limited Warranty</p>"
          }
        },
